title: Trematocranus
text:
Trematocranus is a small <a href="genus">genus</a> of <a href="haplochromine">haplochromine</a> <a href="cichlid">cichlid</a>s <a href="endemism">endemic</a> to <a href="Lake%20Malawi">Lake Malawi</a>.
Species.
